
Entity framework 7 with ASP.NET 5 Core doesn't support edmx. By default it follows code first approach,and we can migrate the existing db using scaffold. It will generate dbcontext as well as poco class.

Steps:
1.Include the following references :
-  "EntityFramework.MicrosoftSqlServer": "7.0.0-rc1-15945",
-  "EntityFramework.MicrosoftSqlServer.Design": "7.0.0-rc1-15945",
-  "EntityFramework.Commands": "7.0.0-rc1-final"
	
2. Add the following in command tag
   "ef": "EntityFramework.Commands"

3. Restore references

4. Open Vs command prompt.Run it as admin
5. Upgrade dnvm command - dnvm upgrade
6. Restore command - dnu restore
7. Scaffold edmx command -dnx ef dbcontext scaffold "Server=.;Database=AEP;Trusted_Connection=True;" EntityFramework.MicrosoftSqlServer
